Group: FedNow Service
Collection: FedNow Service Release 1
Usage Guideline: FedNowParticipantFile_admi.998.001.02
Base Message: admi.998.001.02
Date of publication: 01 June 2023
URL: https://www2.swift.com/mystandards/#/mp/mx/_kijaUKEYEeuB-v2uhrZqSw/_rz7AKZ5FEeyNX8SYmSuaLA
Description: FedNow Service Scope

A FedNow participant file is the message the FedNow Service sends to provide FedNow participants with a list of all FedNow participants and the FedNow services they are enrolled for.

FedNow Service Usage

The FedNow Service will send the participant file to all FedNow participants on an unsolicited basis after the close of the FedNow funds-transfer business day. FedNow participants cannot solicit a participant file during the business day.

